channel.title: [517] toksick525 release! [517]
channel.description:
[size=18pt][u][b]THIS IS MY FIRST RELEASE![/b][/u][/size]
[size=12pt]LEECHERS CAN LEECH! :) [/size]
PICTURES ARE FIRST! [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/i_logo14.png[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/dclawspec.gif[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/dfs.gif[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/hybriding.gif[/img] lol when im walking after i used noclip [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/spec1.gif[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/spec2.gif[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/vengance.gif[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/pvpdrops.gif[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/deepwild.jpg[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/home.jpg[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/rev.jpg[/img] [img]http://i802.photobucket.com/albums/yy301/TOKSICK525/welcome.jpg[/img]
[font=impact][size=18pt][u]!COMMANDS![/u][/size][/font]
ADMIN COMMANDS: ::kill (kills the player they are in combat with) ::admin (spawns basic PVP gear ::suplies (spawns sara brews super restores super set and food) ::pvphybrid (spawns PVP armour hybrid gear) ::hybrid (spawns normal hybrid gear) ::melee (spawns all god swords vesta spear divine shield whip and full vesta) ::banuser ::unbanuser ::ipbanuser ::unipbanuser ::alltome (teleports everyone to whoever uses the command) ::tele Xaxis Yaxis Hight ::teletome <username> ::teleto <username> ::adminc (admin commands) ::veng (gives veng runes) ::gfx (gfx ID) ::emote (emote ID) ::kick <username> ::givemod <username> ::giveadmin <username> ::bow ::dance ::happybday
MOD COMMANDS: ::muteuser <username> ::unmuteuser <username> ::ipmuteuser <username> ::unipmuteuser <username>
NORMAL COMMANDS: ::pvp ::easts ::item (item id) (ammount) ::starter ::Setlevel (level id) (level) ::Toggle (for pures) ::teleports ::checkkills ::sellitem (item id) ::sellall (sells inventory) ::checkprice (item id) ::restorespecial (only works in safe zones ::edgepk ::sit
WEAPON EFFECTS: saradomin god sword heals if you hit with special bandos godsword drains opponents defense when hit with special zamorak godsword freezes opponent
guthans heals randomly per hit dharoks hits hard at random times karils drains opponents defence randomly torag drains opponents run ranomly
AND MUCH MORE i just dont feel like typing everything
FEATURES!: 100% KBD 95% god wars 100% duel arena 80% bounty hunter 95% fight caves 98% clan wars
im not sure what other info i should put ive had this source for a long time so i forget where i got it from the only other info i have is that its stable and its a codeusa base OHOHOHOHOH! ALSO YOU CAN USE ANY 517 CLIENT! I USED INSANE-PKZ CLIENT!
[b][u][font=times new roman][size=24pt]THE REASON I AM RELEASING THIS IS BECAUSE I GOT BORED OF PVP AND MY PLAYERS DEMANDED SOMETHING NEW![/size][/font][/u][/b]
HOW TO CHANGE IP IN CLIENT
First open the client then go to the src folder then look for loader.java and replace the 127.0.0.1 with your no-ip then look for [u]Class68_Sub20_Sub15.java[/u] and change the 127.0.0.1 to you no-ip aswell [/color]ENJOY LEECHERS![color=red][u][color]
DOWNLOAD! http://www.mediafire.com/?9a36gagtr2nom76
!CREDITS! roflscape - 80% me - 20% (fixing alot of bugs)
